---

## 12. Final Clause (Structural Separation Rule)

CNIG may be referenced, studied, and discussed as a conceptual framework.

However:

CNIG must never function as an authority layer over any operational system.

All interpretations must preserve the separation between:

- interpretation (CNIG)  
- execution (system runtime)
